814
00:53:27.167 --> 00:53:28.492
Doc, look.

815
00:53:28.603 --> 00:53:30.519
All we need is a little plutonium.

816
00:53:31.130 --> 00:53:32.844
I am sure that in 1985,

817
00:53:32.965 --> 00:53:35.192
