822
00:53:47.229 --> 00:53:48.313
I got a girl.

823
00:53:48.397 --> 00:53:49.439
Is she pretty?

824
00:53:49.982 --> 00:53:51.343
Doc, she is beautiful.

825
00:53:51.968 --> 00:53:53.668
