01:17:57.160 --> 01:17:58.262
Yeah, well...

1315
01:17:58.974 --> 01:18:00.173
you should not drink.

1316
01:18:00.258 --> 01:18:02.042
Why not?
Because you...

1317
01:18:03.094 --> 01:18:04.519
You might regret it,

1318
01:18:04.920 --> 01:18:06.145
later in life.

1319
01:18:06.889 --> 01:18:08.607
Marty, don't be such a square.

1320
01:18:08.891 --> 01:18:10.809
Everybody who is anybody drinks.

1321
01:18:15.982 --> 01:18:17.516
Jeez, you smoke too?

1322
01:18:19.193 --> 01:18:21.595
Marty, you are beginning
to sound just like my mother.

1323
01:18:33.416 --> 01:18:34.809
<i>We are going to take a little break,</i>

1324
01:18:34.834 --> 01:18:36.798
<i>but we will be back in a while so...</i>

1325
01:18:37.098 --> 01:18:38.837
<i>don't nobody go nowhere.</i>

1326
01:18:55.396 --> 01:18:56.364
Marty?

1327
01:18:57.060 --> 01:18:58.690
Why are you so nervous?

1328
01:18:59.942 --> 01:19:00.942
Lorraine.

1329
01:19:02.236 --> 01:19:03.325
Have you ever...

1330
01:19:05.307 --> 01:19:07.152
been in a situation where you knew,

1331
01:19:07.176 --> 01:19:09.069
you had to act a certain way
but when you...

1332
01:19:09.210 --> 01:19:11.870
got there, you didn't know if
you could go through with it?

1333
01:19:12.455 --> 01:19:15.056
You mean like how you are
supposed to act on a first date?

1334
01:19:16.000 --> 01:19:17.050
Sort of.

1335
01:19:18.040 --> 01:19:20.312
Well, I think, I know exactly
what you mean.

1336
01:19:21.429 --> 01:19:22.429
You do?

1337
01:19:23.341 --> 01:19:25.367
You know what I do in those situations?

1338
01:19:26.052 --> 01:19:26.882
What?

1339
01:19:27.261 --> 01:19:28.303
I don't worry.

1340
01:19:46.322 --> 01:19:47.619
This is all wrong.

1341
01:19:48.501 --> 01:19:50.069
I don't know what it is.

1342
01:19:51.619 --> 01:19:52.621
But when I kiss you,

1343
01:19:53.728 --> 01:19:55.338
it's like I am kissing...

1344
01:19:56.874 --> 01:19:57.949
my brother.

1345
01:19:58.674 --> 01:20:00.816
I guess that doesn't make
any sense, does it?

1346
01:20:01.337 --> 01:20:02.340
Believe me.

1347
01:20:03.805 --> 01:20:05.405
It makes perfect sense.

1348
01:20:06.895 --> 01:20:08.088
Somebody is coming.

1349
01:20:12.807 --> 01:20:16.518
