to my car you son of a bitch.

1350
01:20:17.103 --> 01:20:18.999
And I am going to take it out of your ass.

1351
01:20:19.000 --> 01:20:20.000
Hold him.

1352
01:20:21.315 --> 01:20:23.233
Let him go Biff.
You are drunk.

1353
01:20:24.568 --> 01:20:26.728
Well, look-ey what we have here.

1354
01:20:29.824 --> 01:20:30.902
No, no!

1355
01:20:30.987 --> 01:20:32.651
You are staying right here with me.

1356
01:20:32.876 --> 01:20:34.577
Come on, Lorraine.
Let me go!

1357
01:20:34.662 --> 01:20:35.912
Leave her alone, you bastard!

1358
01:20:35.996 --> 01:20:37.831
Take him in back.
Alright, I will be right there.

1359
01:20:37.915 --> 01:20:39.747
Just admit that you want it.

1360
01:20:40.148 --> 01:20:40.800
Come on.

1361
01:20:41.225 --> 01:20:43.418
Well, go on.
This ain't no peep show.

1362
01:20:50.136 --> 01:20:51.261
Hey, let's put him in there.

1363
01:20:51.345 --> 01:20:52.123
Yeah!

1364
01:20:54.140 --> 01:20:55.671
That's for messing up my hair.

1365
01:20:56.645 --> 01:20:58.382
