1366
01:20:58.728 --> 01:21:01.087
Hey, beat it, spook.
This don't concern you.

1367
01:21:03.774 --> 01:21:06.159
Who you calling spook, peckerwood?

1368
01:21:07.820 --> 01:21:09.055
Hey, hey, listen guys...

1369
01:21:09.572 --> 01:21:11.857
