1387
01:22:03.125 --> 01:22:05.210
Close the door and beat it.

1388
01:22:07.797 --> 01:22:08.910
No Biff.

1389
01:22:09.853 --> 01:22:11.405
You leave her alone.

1390
01:22:12.134 --> 01:22:13.427
Alright McFly.

1391
01:22:17.181 --> 01:22:18.460
You are asking for it,

1392
01:22:19.278 --> 01:22:20.709
