to the living room rug,

1481
01:30:52.204 --> 01:30:53.430
go easy on him.

1482
01:30:54.699 --> 01:30:55.699
Ok.

1483
01:31:00.872 --> 01:31:01.919
Marty.

1484
01:31:02.531 --> 01:31:03.807
Such a nice name.

1485
01:31:09.672 --> 01:31:11.298
Damn!
Where is that kid?

1486
01:31:15.011 --> 01:31:15.812
Damn!

1487
01:31:18.723 --> 01:31:19.798
Damn! Damn!

1488
01:31:27.940 --> 01:31:28.959
You are late!

1489
01:31:28.960 --> 01:31:30.817
Do you have no concept of time?

1490
01:31:30.902 --> 01:31:32.057
Hey, come on.

1491
01:31:32.236 --> 01:31:33.338
I had to change.

1492
01:31:33.363 --> 01:31:35.847
Do you think I am going back
in that zoot suit?

1493
01:31:36.961 --> 01:31:39.093
The old man really came through.
It worked.

1494
01:31:39.118 --> 01:31:41.003
What?
He laid out Biff in one punch.

1495
01:31:41.287 --> 01:31:42.523
I didn't know he had it in him.

1496
01:31:42.548 --> 01:31:44.458
He is never stood up to Biff in his life.

1497
01:31:47.043 --> 01:31:47.912
Never?

1498
01:31:48.294 --> 01:31:50.045
No. Why?
What's the matter?

1499
01:31:51.130 --> 01:31:52.023
Alright!

1500
01:31:52.678 --> 01:31:54.841
Let's set your destination time.

1501
01:31:59.597 --> 01:32:01.497
This is the exact time you left.

1502
01:32:02.308 --> 01:32:03.881
Let's send you back,

1503
01:32:03.905 --> 01:32:05.769
at exactly the same time.

1504
01:32:08.733 --> 01:32:10.184
It will be like you never left.

1505
01:32:12.610 --> 01:32:13.513
Now,

1506
01:32:13.774 --> 01:32:16.885
I painted a white line
on the street way over there.

1507
01:32:17.115 --> 01:32:18.690
That's where you will start from.

1508
01:32:19.075 --> 01:32:21.410
I have calculated the precise distance,

1509
01:32:21.494 --> 01:32:24.086
taking into account
the acceleration speed,

1510
01:32:24.180 --> 01:32:26.904
and wind resistance retroactive
from the moment,

1511
01:32:26.928 --> 01:32:28.408
the lightning strikes,

1512
01:32:28.793 --> 01:32:29.865
which will be...

1513
01:32:30.063 --> 01:32:31.283
in exactly,

1514
01:32:31.307 --> 01:32:33.296
7 minutes and 22 seconds.

1515
01:32:33.673 --> 01:32:36.171
When this alarm goes off,
you hit the gas.

1516
01:32:36.196 --> 01:32:36.990
Right.

1517
01:32:44.016 --> 01:32:44.745
Well...

1518
01:32:45.267 --> 01:32:46.893
I guess that's everything.

1519
01:32:51.274 --> 01:32:52.229
Thanks.

1520
01:32:52.817 --> 01:32:53.784
Thank you.

1521
01:32:59.031 --> 01:33:00.958
See you in about 30 years.

1522
01:33:02.869 --> 01:33:04.002
I hope so.

1523
01:33:05.872 --> 01:33:07.214
Don't worry!

1524
01:33:08.082 --> 01:33:09.851
As long as you hit that wire

1525
01:33:09.876 --> 01:33:12.961
with the connecting hook at
precisely 88 miles an hour,

1526
01:33:13.045 --> 01:33:15.647
the instant the lightning strikes
the tower...

1527
01:33:18.509 --> 01:33:19.769
everything will be fine.

1528
01:33:19.916 --> 01:33:20.683
Right.

1529
01:33:29.770 --> 01:33:31.330
What's the meaning of this?

1530
01:33:31.873 --> 01:33:33.541
You will find out in 30 years.

1531
01:33:33.566 --> 01:33:35.650
It's about the future, isn't it?

1532
01:33:35.882 --> 01:33:38.379
It's information about the future.
Wait a minute.

1533
01:33:38.529 --> 01:33:40.447
