1537
01:33:49.248 --> 01:33:52.801
I refuse to accept the responsibility.

1538
01:33:52.919 --> 01:33:55.403
In that case, I will tell you straight out.

1539
01:33:59.634 --> 01:34:00.951
Great Scott!

1540
01:34:08.976 --> 01:34:10.716
You get the cable,

1541
01:34:10.740 --> 01:34:13.499
I will throw the rope down to you.
