1542
01:34:48.099 --> 01:34:49.083
Doc!

1543
01:34:57.042 --> 01:34:58.626
Come on, come on.
Let's go!

1544
01:34:58.651 --> 01:34:59.647
Alright!

1545
01:35:00.048 --> 01:35:01.119
Take it up!

1546
01:35:04.532 --> 01:35:05.328
Go!

1547
01:35:12.707 --> 01:35:13.607
Doc!

1548
01:35:13.991 --> 01:35:14.819
What?

1549
01:35:14.961 --> 01:35:18.296
I have to tell you about the future.

1550
01:35:18.530 --> 01:35:19.217
What?

1551
01:35:19.242 --> 01:35:22.912
I have to tell you about the future!

1552
01:35:23.009 --> 01:35:23.868
What?

1553
01:35:24.427 --> 01:35:27.167
On the night I go back...

1554
01:35:27.464 --> 01:35:29.437
in time, you get...

1555
01:35:32.768 --> 01:35:33.719
Doc!

1556
01:35:43.279 --> 01:35:44.187
Go!

1557
01:35:45.349 --> 01:35:46.364
No Doc!

1558
01:35:46.532 --> 01:35:47.842
Look at the time!

1559
01:35:47.867 --> 01:35:50.005
You have got less than four minutes.

1560
01:35:50.082 --> 01:35:51.842
Please, hurry!

1561
01:36:03.466 --> 01:36:04.700
Yeah!

1562
01:36:58.020 --> 01:37:00.814
Dammit Doc!
Why did you have to tear up that letter?

1563
01:37:01.399 --> 01:37:02.758
If I only had more time.

1564
01:37:06.362 --> 01:37:07.437
Wait a minute.

1565
01:37:07.738 --> 01:37:09.671
I got all the time I want.
