1566
01:37:09.672 --> 01:37:12.109
I can just go back early and warn him.

1567
01:37:12.368 --> 01:37:13.182
Ok.

1568
01:37:13.308 --> 01:37:14.636
Ten minutes ought to do it.

1569
01:37:17.586 --> 01:37:18.795
Time circuit's on.

1570
01:37:19.123 --> 01:37:20.363
Flux capacitor...

1571
01:37:21.116 --> 01:37:22.147
