Engine running.

1573
01:37:23.487 --> 01:37:24.374
Alright.

1574
01:37:27.258 --> 01:37:28.038
No.

1575
01:37:28.351 --> 01:37:29.589
No, no, no.

1576
01:37:30.845 --> 01:37:33.054
Come on. Not this time.
Come on. Come on.

1577
01:38:43.501 --> 01:38:44.383
Come on.

1578
01:38:46.816 --> 01:38:47.985
Here we go. Here we go.

1579
01:38:48.049 --> 01:38:49.406
