Hello.
Good morning.

1647
01:47:57.095 --> 01:47:57.751
Mom!

1648
01:47:58.048 --> 01:47:58.769
Dad!

1649
01:47:59.098 --> 01:48:00.580
Did you hit your head?
Marty, are you alright?

1650
01:48:00.767 --> 01:48:01.547
You guys,

1651
01:48:01.571 --> 01:48:02.884
you guys look great.

1652
01:48:02.962 --> 01:48:04.791
Mom, you look so thin.

1653
01:48:05.072 --> 01:48:06.212
Thank you Marty.

1654
01:48:06.745 --> 01:48:07.847
George!

1655
01:48:09.108 --> 01:48:10.493
Good morning, sleepyhead.

1656
01:48:12.111 --> 01:48:13.963
Good morning Dave.
Good morning Mom.

1657
01:48:13.988 --> 01:48:14.771
Linda.

1658
01:48:15.031 --> 01:48:17.532
Oh Marty, I almost forgot.
Jennifer Parker called.

1659
01:48:17.624 --> 01:48:19.097
I sure like her Marty.

1660
01:48:19.121 --> 01:48:21.251
She is such a sweet girl.

1661
01:48:21.788 --> 01:48:23.789
Isn't tonight the night of the big date?

1662
01:48:23.873 --> 01:48:25.281
