1670
01:48:37.214 --> 01:48:38.400
Why was not I told?
Quiet down.

1671
01:48:38.425 --> 01:48:39.554
I am sure the car is fine.

1672
01:48:39.579 --> 01:48:41.830
Why am I always the last
one to know about these things?

1673
01:48:41.855 --> 01:48:44.341
See? There is Biff out there
waxing it right now.

1674
01:48:45.419 --> 01:48:47.024
Now Biff, I want to make sure that

1675
01:48:47.049 --> 01:48:49.591
we get two coats of wax this time,
not just one.

1676
01:48:49.844 --> 01:48:51.428
I am just finishing up the second coat now.

1677
01:48:51.453 --> 01:48:52.306
Now Biff,

1678
01:48:52.572 --> 01:48:54.005
don't con me.

1679
01:48:55.655 --> 01:48:57.510
I am. I am sorry, Mr. McFly.

1680
01:48:57.719 --> 01:49:00.504
I meant I was just,
just starting on the second coat.

1681
01:49:01.330 --> 01:49:03.455
Yeah Biff. What a character.

1682
01:49:03.756 --> 01:49:05.883
Always trying to get away with something.

1683
01:49:06.290 --> 01:49:08.551
I have had to stay on top of Biff
