I think it's your new book.

1690
01:49:23.122 --> 01:49:24.029
Honey.

1691
01:49:24.269 --> 01:49:26.085
Your first novel.

1692
01:49:27.270 --> 01:49:29.384
Like I have always told you,
you put your mind to it,

1693
01:49:29.408 --> 01:49:31.198
